      "name": "Common Questions",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<section class=\"fp-faq-section\">\n  <div class=\"fp-faq-inner\">\n    <small class=\"overline module-header_overline text-size-tiny uppercase text-color-tertiary margin-bottom margin-xxsmall mobile-margin-xsmall text-weight-semibold\">Common questions</small>\n    <h2 class=\"fp-faq-title\">Probably wondering…</h2>\n\n    <div class=\"fp-faq-grid\">\n      <div class=\"fp-faq-item\">\n        <div class=\"fp-faq-q\">Is this just corporate gifting with a fancier name?</div>\n        <div class=\"fp-faq-a\">No. Corporate gifting is a product - you buy it, it ships, done. A relationship moments program is a strategy. We design the touchpoints across your client lifecycle, source the gifts, personalize them, manage the delivery, and review the program with you quarterly. You end up with a system. Not a to-do list.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"fp-faq-item\">\n        <div class=\"fp-faq-q\">How is this different from Baskits or any other gifting company?</div>\n        <div class=\"fp-faq-a\">Baskits and other gifting companies think about <em>what</em> to send. We think about <em>when</em> to show up, <em>why</em> it matters to that specific relationship, and how to make it happen consistently across your entire client base. They're product companies. We're a relationship partner.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"fp-faq-item\">\n        <div class=\"fp-faq-q\">We already spend money on client gifts. Does this replace that?</div>\n        <div class=\"fp-faq-a\">Yes - and your budget goes further. We take what's currently ad hoc, reactive spending and turn it into a strategic program with better gifts, better timing, and better outcomes. Most clients find their total spend stays the same or decreases while the impact increases significantly.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"fp-faq-item\">\n        <div class=\"fp-faq-q\">Do you ship across North America?</div>\n        <div class=\"fp-faq-a\">We handle all logistics, anywhere in North America. Every gift is sourced from Canadian-made, women-owned, and sustainable brands - so what you send reflects well on you and your values.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"fp-faq-item\">\n        <div class=\"fp-faq-q\">How long does it take to get started?</div>\n        <div class=\"fp-faq-a\">Most programs are up and running within 4–6 weeks. That includes your Moments Mapping session, gift curation, and first delivery. We'll walk you through every step.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"fp-faq-item\">\n        <div class=\"fp-faq-q\">What if we only have a few key relationships right now?</div>\n        <div class=\"fp-faq-a\">That's exactly who the Focus program is for. Ten relationships done right is more valuable than fifty done inconsistently. </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .fp-faq-section {\n    background: #FFFFFF;\n    padding: 80px 48px;\n  }\n  .fp-faq-inner {\n    max-width: 1120px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n  .fp-faq-title {\n    font-size: 40px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #1F3323;\n    margin-bottom: 48px;\n    line-height: 1.15;\n    letter-spacing: -0.5px;\n  }\n  .fp-faq-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 32px;\n  }\n  .fp-faq-q {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #1F3323;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  .fp-faq-a {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #5C5C5C;\n    line-height: 1.65;\n  }\n  .fp-faq-a a {\n    color: #C0552A;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    font-weight: 500;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .fp-faq-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    .fp-faq-section { padding: 60px 24px; }\n    .fp-faq-title { font-size: 28px; }\n  }\n</style>",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "padding_top": 40,
        "padding_bottom": 52
      }
    },
